This is incorrect, you want to be increasing _letter_ by _&amp;Delta;n_; and not at the declaration.

And, you are then casting _castAscii_ to a _char_.  
I would remove _ch_ and simply cast _castAscii_ when it&#39;s appended to _output_.

```java
output += (char) castAscii
```

